85
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,540
Yes.

86
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:57,370
Please wait for me for a moment.

87
00:05:58,070 --> 00:05:58,530
Please.

88
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:15,690
Everything is normal.

89
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:18,120
Everything is normal.

90
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,830
