94
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,600
Hello, Mr. Zhou.

95
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,160
I'm Zhu Yifei.

96
00:07:09,410 --> 00:07:10,100
Mr. Zhu.

97
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,270
Mr. Zhou, even you didn't think

98
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,550
