blending into the crowd.

102
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:24,430
Mr. Zhu, your way of doing things
really is

103
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,480
different.

104
00:07:39,990 --> 00:07:41,590
-Uncle Yifei.
-Uncle Yifei.

105
00:08:03,270 --> 00:08:05,430
Dear Mr. Zhou, sorry

106
00:08:05,450 --> 00:08:06,560
