110
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:11,510
Zheng!

111
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,120
Here!

112
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:12,700
Chubby!

113
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:13,160
Here!

114
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:13,750
Scrawny!

115
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:14,240
Here!

116
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,750
We are all family.

117
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,240
Mr. Zhu, you act with such caution.

118
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,120
It's truly admirable.

119
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:23,510
Well, actually, I get motion sickness
