130
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:54,480
Got it.

131
00:08:55,870 --> 00:08:56,670
Let's go, bro.

132
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,720
Please go inside.

133
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:00,960
Don't stand on ceremony.

134
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,890
Please, please.

135
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:10,250
