136
00:09:22,270 --> 00:09:23,400
Please, have a seat.

137
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:36,280
Mr. Zhou.

138
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:01,210
Keep watch.

139
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,600
Mr. Zhou,

140
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:23,240
