141
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,940
I usually

142
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:27,090
keep a low profile.

143
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,580
This time I came in person,

144
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:30,910
