145
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:33,550
this deal involves
a significant amount of money,

146
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,610
and second because

147
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:37,450
I wanted to meet you myself, Mr. Zhou.

148
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,960
You're young and promising, Mr. Zhou.

149
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:42,090
We've made the right decision to come.

150
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:42,890
Alright.

151
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,510
I plan to stay in Sanjiangkou

152
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,390
