165
00:13:35,030 --> 00:13:37,030
without showing the shape of the money.

166
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,430
Just an extra mechanism.

167
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,210
-High-tech.
-High-tech.

168
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,760
Can't you just pour it all in?

169
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:44,510
What now?

170
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:48,000
Now,

171
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:50,550
I'll take my leave first.

172
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:52,980
In half an hour,

173
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:55,800
