in person.

174
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:56,670
Leave?

175
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,270
You want to leave?

176
00:14:58,270 --> 00:14:59,750
But I haven't even seen the goods yet.

177
00:14:59,750 --> 00:15:00,550
That's right.

178
00:15:00,910 --> 00:15:02,030
In half an hour,

179
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,460
