180
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:06,710
Then please, Mr. Zhu,

181
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:08,110
stay for another half hour with me.

182
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:09,600
So you still don't trust me.

183
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,330
Well, I haven't seen the goods.

184
00:15:12,350 --> 00:15:17,820
♪ Doubt ♪

185
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,850
Here's the thing, Mr. Zhou.

186
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:22,890
I never do transactions with the goods
right in front of me.

187
00:15:22,890 --> 00:15:23,980
That's my rule.

188
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,130
Please understand.

189
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,720
I also have my rule:

190
00:15:26,910 --> 00:15:28,290
cash on delivery.

191
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:30,180
One million is not a small amount.

192
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,980
If I don't see the goods today,

193
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,600
you, you,

194
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,260
and all the vehicles—

195
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:36,590
