196
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:43,200
And if I refuse?

197
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:16,730
It wasn't me.

198
00:16:17,030 --> 00:16:18,230
It wasn't me, either.

199
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:20,550
Then it must've been Mr. Zhu.

200
00:16:20,550 --> 00:16:21,680
It must've been you.

201
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:22,960
Bro.

202
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,440
Is your last name Huo?

203
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:29,140
Your mentor's cousin

204
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:30,750
and my second aunt's nephew

205
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:32,010
are brothers-in-law.

206
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:33,230
In that case,

207
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:35,010
we are also relatives.

208
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:38,600
There's a place for entertainment

209
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:40,120
in the basement of Fenglinwan Hotel.

210
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,350
If you guys are interested,

211
00:16:41,350 --> 00:16:42,060
you can go find

212
00:16:42,060 --> 00:16:43,460
a manager surnamed Zhou.

213
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:45,600
She'll make the arrangements for you.

214
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:48,000
Try the services in Sanjiangkou, alright?

215
00:16:57,030 --> 00:16:58,490
If this deal goes through,

216
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:00,250
it'll be good for both of us,

217
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:01,360
right?

218
00:17:15,790 --> 00:17:17,750
My mentor does have a cousin.

219
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:18,920
I made it up.

220
00:17:20,829 --> 00:17:22,720
Since there's a family connection here,

221
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:24,599
we can talk things through.

222
00:17:26,109 --> 00:17:27,970
I'm willing to make an exception.

223
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:31,100
Thank you then, Mr. Zhu.

224
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:32,580
Please sit.

225
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:33,920
Okay.

226
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:53,510
[Protect Forest Resources,
Strictly Prevent Forest Fires]

227
00:17:53,890 --> 00:17:56,140
[Depart in 15 minutes.]

228
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,120
Depart in 15 minutes.

229
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:58,320
[Go to Zhou Rong's villa.
Sturdy will meet you there.]

230
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:57,200
Go to Zhou Rong's villa.

231
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,240
Sturdy will meet you there.

232
00:17:58,240 --> 00:17:59,160
Got it.

233
00:17:58,340 --> 00:18:00,350
[Got it.]

234
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:10,530
[Photographs of Cultural Relics]

235
00:18:10,530 --> 00:18:13,570
[Purchase Receipt]

236
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:16,830
Why are you driving so slow?

237
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:17,630
Drive faster.

238
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:26,690
Boss.

239
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,180
I-I need to take this call.

240
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:31,200
You'd better not use your phone
while driving.

241
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,350
But it's my boss calling.

242
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,080
He must need something from me.

243
00:18:36,510 --> 00:18:37,570
[Gai]

244
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:40,000
Gai, I'll be there in a few minutes.

245
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:40,750
The owner of Jinxin Repair Shop

246
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:41,560
