248
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:44,350
He said there's a Xiali taxi

249
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,950
with its rear bumper dented.

250
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:47,790
That must be them, Gai.

251
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:49,680
Can you ask the owner

252
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,940
to stall them for a bit?

253
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,070
I'll head over once I'm done here.

254
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:52,530
No need.

255
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:54,490
I know those two bastards.

256
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:55,880
As soon as I'm done here,

257
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:56,750
I'll take you to their house

258
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,610
to corner them.

259
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,790
[Protect Forest Resources,
Strictly Prevent Forest Fires]

260
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:58,880
Thanks, Gai.

261
00:18:59,420 --> 00:18:59,960
Got it.

262
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:01,440
[Gai]

263
00:19:00,750 --> 00:19:01,280
Alright.

264
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,170
Did we crash?

265
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:12,030
[Loyalty]

266
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,310
Okay.

267
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:15,210
Okay, got it.

268
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:16,590
The fresh produce truck
that delivered food

269
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:17,550
