279
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:35,450
The bianzhong has arrived.

280
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,210
The bianzhong has arrived.

281
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:40,110
Let's go!

282
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:47,480
Buddy,

283
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,860
