284
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,070
How could you just

285
00:19:51,070 --> 00:19:53,130
park on the side of the road like that?

286
00:19:53,270 --> 00:19:54,730
Did you rear-end me or not?

287
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,400
Yes.

288
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,830
I should take full responsibility.

289
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:07,540
What are you doing?

290
00:20:08,270 --> 00:20:09,400
Calling the police.

291
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,640
Let's not trouble the police.

292
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,040
It's such a small matter.

293
00:20:14,070 --> 00:20:15,600
We can settle it ourselves.

294
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:19,690
Let's just leave it at that.

295
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,570
Leave it at that?

296
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,530
I'm easy to talk to.

297
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:39,720
If it were someone else,

298
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:41,720
you wouldn't be able to leave today.

299
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:42,440
Buddy.

300
00:20:45,790 --> 00:20:47,570
This is a Mercedes.

301
00:20:48,590 --> 00:20:49,670
What can

302
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:51,160
100 yuan even cover?

303
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:56,720
How much do you want?

304
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,570
Since this guy is willing to pay,

305
00:20:58,570 --> 00:21:00,170
I should ask for at least 500.

306
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:06,930
Look at this—

307
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:08,290
the bumper is smashed.

308
00:21:09,740 --> 00:21:10,910
At the very least,

309
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,680
it's going to cost this much.

310
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,480
Where am I supposed to steal

311
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,540
5,000 yuan for you?

312
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:20,690
If you can't steal

313
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:21,720
5,000 yuan for me,

314
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:23,800
t-then I'll call the police.

315
00:21:24,510 --> 00:21:25,400
What do you want?

316
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:26,460
What are you doing?

317
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,740
Your car crashed mine!

318
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,020
What are you doing?

319
00:21:30,420 --> 00:21:32,820
A gentleman uses his tongue,
not his fists!

320
00:21:33,070 --> 00:21:33,640
We can talk this over.

321
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:34,660
A gentleman uses his tongue,
not his fists!

322
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:35,460
A gentleman uses his tongue...

323
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:36,920
A gentleman uses his tongue,
not his fists.

324
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:39,320
A gentleman uses his tongue,
not his fists.

325
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:41,310
Isn't this just about 5,000 yuan?

326
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:41,840
I'll pay.

327
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:43,010
Alright?

328
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:43,920
Boss,

329
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,200
what does this have to do with you?

330
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,510
He's paying me 5,000.

331
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,800
What kind of situation is this?

332
00:21:52,270 --> 00:21:54,160
You think I don't know traffic rules?

333
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,360
This is rear-ending.

334
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:57,420
You're supposed to
take full responsibility.

335
00:21:57,420 --> 00:21:58,080
Keep quiet.

336
00:22:01,930 --> 00:22:02,530
Sir,

337
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:03,470
it's our fault.

338
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:06,330
I'll give you 5,000 yuan,

339
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,460
but don't call the police.

340
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:10,460
Okay.

341
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:15,480
Only 5,000?

342
00:22:20,590 --> 00:22:21,210
10,000?

343
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:23,280
10,000?

344
00:22:23,690 --> 00:22:24,910
I'll give you 10,000,

345
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:27,090
but promise you won't call the police.

346
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,150
Wait,

347
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:32,930
why should you give him money?

348
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:33,920
Boss.

349
00:22:35,790 --> 00:22:36,270
50,000.

350
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:39,270
One penny less and I'll call the cops.

351
00:22:39,270 --> 00:22:40,200
You little runt.

352
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,270
How can you be so shameless?

353
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:42,400
Why are you talking so...

354
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,550
Why are you talking so...

355
00:22:43,550 --> 00:22:44,110
See if I dare to call the police!

356
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:44,590
50,000!

357
00:22:45,550 --> 00:22:46,280
50,000 it is!

358
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,690
I agree.

359
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:48,480
Okay.

360
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:51,450
But I don't have that much cash
on me right now.

361
00:22:51,480 --> 00:22:51,920
Go and

362
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,750
give Mr. Zhou a call.

363
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:55,200
Tell him to bring the money right away.

364
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:55,880
Hurry up!

365
00:22:56,070 --> 00:22:57,000
Just ignore him.

366
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:58,030
He wouldn't dare.

367
00:22:58,030 --> 00:22:58,840
Watch me!

368
00:22:59,000 --> 00:22:59,800
Make the call!

369
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,550
Make the call!

370
00:23:00,550 --> 00:23:01,590
Why do you have so much to say?

371
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:02,270
You're really...

372
00:23:02,270 --> 00:23:03,710
It's no big deal. You...

373
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:04,920
Just let him call the police.

374
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:05,830
Pay to avoid trouble, okay?

375
00:23:05,280 --> 00:23:07,090
[Photographs of Cultural Relics]

376
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:07,160
Pay to avoid trouble.

377
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,310
He wouldn't dare at all.

378
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:09,170
What if he does?

379
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:10,910
Look at his runty face.

380
00:23:10,010 --> 00:23:12,140
[Purchase Receipt]

381
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:19,300
2.5 million.

382
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,330
[2.5 million yuan]

383
00:23:19,410 --> 00:23:20,420
I'll give you 800,000.

384
00:23:19,690 --> 00:23:22,820
[800,000 yuan]

385
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,130
For such a big deal,

386
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:23,440
you say you'll give me 800,000.

387
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,590
Then what do you make?

388
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:26,070
You think I'm doing this for money?

389
00:23:25,940 --> 00:23:26,600
[Purchase Receipt]

390
00:23:26,600 --> 00:23:27,010
[Its estimated value is 43 million yuan.]

391
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:30,830
That Mr. Zhou you just mentioned—

392
00:23:30,830 --> 00:23:32,890
is he Zhou Rong from Rongcheng Group?

393
00:23:33,270 --> 00:23:33,680
Who?

394
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,240
Is he?

395
00:23:35,560 --> 00:23:36,490
I don't know him.

396
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:38,850
I don't know him.

397
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,050
How dare he lie to me?

398
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:55,750
Mr. Zhu.

399
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:57,340
How much longer

400
00:23:57,590 --> 00:23:58,590
do we have to wait?

401
00:23:59,510 --> 00:24:01,200
That bastard Liu Bei ran off.

402
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,530
Have the goods arrived?

403
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,510
We ran into a bit of trouble

404
00:24:13,750 --> 00:24:15,280
during the transportation

405
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:18,270
of the goods.

406
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:19,300
How about this?

407
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:20,030
Mr. Zhou,

408
00:24:20,270 --> 00:24:22,130
you keep the money for now.

409
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:23,620
Once I've dealt with it,

410
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,120
I'll contact you right away.

411
00:24:25,120 --> 00:24:26,810
So what kind of problem is it?

412
00:24:27,030 --> 00:24:27,960
Just a minor issue—

413
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:28,790
easy to fix.

414
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:30,270
Mr. Zhu, I...

415
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:30,990
You two.

416
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:35,720
Stay.

417
00:24:42,590 --> 00:24:43,680
They just left like that?

418
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:46,110
Wait, those two were here
to pull a fast one, weren't they?

419
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,910
Trying to scam me, weren't they?

420
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:51,500
That shouldn't be.

421
00:24:52,110 --> 00:24:53,000
Is Zhu Yifei not planning

422
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:54,860
to stay in this business anymore?

423
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:59,790
L-L-Let Fang Yong go back first.

424
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:30,240
Are we getting back on the road or not?

425
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:31,470
Yes, yes, we are.

426
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:35,550
Let me take this call.

427
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:37,630
Ren.

428
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:39,440
I'm on my way.

429
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:40,610
It went well.

430
00:25:41,310 --> 00:25:42,030
Very well.

431
00:25:42,590 --> 00:25:43,310
Got it.

432
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:46,510
What now?

433
00:25:51,680 --> 00:25:53,210
The deal's been called off.

434
00:25:53,550 --> 00:25:54,110
My boss told me

435
00:25:54,110 --> 00:25:55,570
to take you straight home.

436
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:57,550
No need to meet the boss anymore.

437
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,520
Rong.

438
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:11,200
What are you looking for? Let me help you.

439
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:13,600
Do you have a charging cable
for this phone?

440
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:18,550
Pull.

441
00:26:30,030 --> 00:26:30,920
This is about it.

442
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:31,850
This could work.

443
00:26:38,350 --> 00:26:38,950
It worked.

444
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:39,760
It worked.

445
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:41,310
It worked. It worked.

446
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:41,960
It worked.

447
00:26:41,940 --> 00:26:44,100
♪ The sun is setting ♪

448
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,840
Let's try again, bro.

449
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:51,000
Again.

450
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:07,310
What the hell.

451
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,330
Lang Bowen's phone?

452
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:11,160
Wasn't this phone smashed

453
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:11,820
and burned?

454
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:13,440
Exactly. D-Didn't I smash it?

455
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:14,000
You did.

456
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:15,440
I saw it with my own eyes

457
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:16,570
that you smashed it.

458
00:27:16,750 --> 00:27:17,880
How is it back again?

459
00:27:19,330 --> 00:27:21,530
The right side is too high. Move it down.

460
00:27:22,230 --> 00:27:23,420
Let me see.

461
00:27:27,090 --> 00:27:28,290
A bit more. A bit more.

462
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:30,340
Still too high. Move it down a bit.

463
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:32,880
All of you, get out.

464
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:33,640
We're almost done here, Rong.

465
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,200
Get out!

466
00:27:35,310 --> 00:27:36,390
Leave. Go on.

467
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:37,160
Hurry up!

468
00:27:40,210 --> 00:27:41,680
That guy Lu has been causing trouble

469
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:42,750
for you again and again.

470
00:27:42,750 --> 00:27:43,920
He even went after Ye Jian.

471
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:45,350
You said it yourself to kill him,

472
00:27:45,350 --> 00:27:46,240
to let him know who's in charge

473
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,000
in Sanjiangkou.

474
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,600
I was just saying it offhand!

475
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:54,600
Come on, give it to me.

476
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:55,640
Rong!

477
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:05,940
Huo Zheng

478
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:08,090
picked it up from the ground just now.

479
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:09,750
Amazing.

480
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:12,680
It's been there for 6 months
and we never noticed it,

481
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:14,610
but he saw it a-as soon as he came in?

482
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:15,330
This is...

483
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:16,250
Unreasonable,

484
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:17,770
isn't it?

485
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:19,530
It's way too unreasonable.

486
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:22,750
Before they came,

487
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:24,350
I had someone clean the room.

488
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,370
I'll go ask them

489
00:28:25,370 --> 00:28:27,030
if anyone has seen this phone.

490
00:29:04,070 --> 00:29:04,800
How did it go?

491
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:05,880
No one saw it.

492
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:06,850
Right?

493
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:08,270
It's obvious that this phone

494
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:09,590
was brought by Zhu Yifei himself.

495
00:29:09,590 --> 00:29:10,510
But how did they even get

496
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:11,170
this phone?

497
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:12,170
How would I know?

498
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,030
That guy Huo just came in

499
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:14,330
and gave me the phone!

500
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,680
Rong, did you take your medication today?

501
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:17,550
What medication!

502
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:19,110
Things are getting
more and more confusing now!

503
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:19,880
That Zhu Yifei came in

504
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:20,920
acting all mysterious, right?

505
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:21,960
One moment this guy is Mr. Zhu,

506
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:22,880
the next moment that guy is Mr. Zhu.

507
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:24,280
Is he crazy or something?

508
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,000
I can't figure out

509
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:26,890
Zhu Yifei's

510
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:27,480
game,

511
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,160
but that guy he brought,

512
00:29:29,160 --> 00:29:30,640
Huo Zheng, is a badass.

513
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:33,030
His nickname is "Huoxiang Zhengqi Water."

514
00:29:33,030 --> 00:29:34,720
He used to be a professional hitman

515
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,550
and has several lives on his hands.

516
00:29:36,550 --> 00:29:37,960
He's been out of sight
for the past few years,

517
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:38,550
and who knows

518
00:29:38,550 --> 00:29:38,960
why he ended up working for

519
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:39,920
that Zhu guy.

520
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:42,880
Zhu Yifei

521
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:45,090
wants to kill me?

522
00:29:45,790 --> 00:29:47,250
But I have no beef with him!

523
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:51,160
Rong,

524
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:52,750
maybe we should put

525
00:29:52,750 --> 00:29:54,680
the matter of the bianzhong
on hold for a bit.

526
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:56,540
I feel like it's too complicated.

527
00:29:57,110 --> 00:29:58,970
The deal can be put on hold for now,

528
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:01,310
but we can't just stay here
like sitting ducks.

529
00:30:01,310 --> 00:30:02,030
Have Li Penggai

530
00:30:02,030 --> 00:30:03,070
stay here with a few people to keep watch.

531
00:30:03,070 --> 00:30:04,530
You take everyone else out

532
00:30:04,550 --> 00:30:05,750
and go find Zhu Yifei.

533
00:30:06,070 --> 00:30:07,270
And after we find him?

534
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,460
After you find him,

535
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:09,690
don't alert him.

536
00:30:09,830 --> 00:30:11,290
Figure out what he's up to.

537
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:13,280
If he dares to move against me...

538
00:30:13,590 --> 00:30:14,320
Understood.

539
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:32,860
It worked, bro.

540
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:33,540
Put me down.

541
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:36,400
Here.

542
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:37,040
Alright.

543
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:38,780
Bro,

544
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:39,870
I'll go first.

545
00:30:40,110 --> 00:30:40,870
No.

546
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:42,680
I'm worried the rope might not be
strong enough.

547
00:30:42,680 --> 00:30:43,660
I'll go up first.

548
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:15,310
Come on, bro. Come up.

549
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:18,730
Come up. Come on.

550
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:30,960
A bit higher.

551
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:47,880
Bro,

552
00:31:50,270 --> 00:31:51,720
let's go down the mountain

553
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:52,780
and find some food.

554
00:31:54,110 --> 00:31:55,510
Why go down the mountain?

555
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:01,270
We're going in during the day?

556
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,070
What's wrong?

557
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:05,420
It's such a big estate—

558
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:06,070
there are definitely people

559
00:32:06,070 --> 00:32:07,240
guarding it.

560
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:08,240
People?

561
00:32:10,030 --> 00:32:11,760
I'm so hungry I'd eat anything.

562
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:13,220
Eat people?

563
00:32:13,670 --> 00:32:15,600
I couldn't bring myself to do that.

564
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:19,700
You're still bound by morals and ethics.

565
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,590
Open a history book—

566
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:25,810
every page is filled with stories of
people eating people.

567
00:32:26,590 --> 00:32:27,850
Bro, let me.

568
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:38,830
My turn.

569
00:32:47,830 --> 00:32:48,360
Let's go.

570
00:33:11,070 --> 00:33:11,510
Bro.

571
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,680
They've all left.

572
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:15,480
Our chance has come.

573
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:20,570
It's God's will.

574
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:23,480
These past few days, God has been

575
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:25,070
testing our patience.

576
00:34:03,260 --> 00:34:05,740
♪ Bunny, bunny, bunny, bunny,
bunny, bunny ♪

577
00:34:06,700 --> 00:34:08,030
♪ Love you, love you, love you ♪

